# Loops

```js
for (let i = 1; i <= 5; i++) {
  console.log("Count:", i);
}
```

A `while` loop runs as long as its condition stays true:

```js
let n = 3;
while (n > 0) {
  console.log(n);
  n--;
}
```

:::try
```js
